Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Cadence Property Group is pleased to offer for sale or lease the last remaining lots within the Altona Logistics Park:

- Lot 23 (63-65 Toll Drive): 30,160 sqm*.
- Lot 8 (58-86 Toll Drive): 21,310 sqm*.

Centered in Melbourne's foremost industrial and logistics precinct, this unique opportunity represents one of the last chances to secure a position in this tightly held location.

Strategically located within close proximity to the Port of Melbourne, multiple freeway on and off ramps and the Melbourne CBD, the Altona Logistics Park is well regarded as the west's premier logistics address.

This significant offering can be summarised by the following key attributes:

- Closest major logistics precinct to the Port of Melbourne (8km) and Melbourne CBD (12km).
- Close proximity to West Gate and Princes Freeway.
- Access and egress from three separate roads including a fully signalised intersection at Grieve Parade.
- Unencumbered truck movements on the extra wide 15m carriageway of Toll Drive with room for truck parking each side of road as well as 2-way traffic.
- Super B-Double approved location.
- No curfew on operating hours.
- Located just over 2km from Altona's main retail strip of Pier Street.
- Benefit from technological advantages of Fibre Optic servicing.

Contact us today about straight land sales, pre-leases, turnkeys and land and building packages.

*approx.

Opportunities for pre-leases, land and building packages or land sales to suit your business or investment strategy.

Within close proximity to all Melbourne's major western freeways, the Port of Melbourne, train stations and public transport networks and the future Altona Inland Port.

- Lots from 2,000sqm or cut to suit.

- Purpose built facilities to your specification.
